{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack","text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pack","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNOfflineStorage.h@T@MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"pack","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The offline pack to remove."}]}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The completion handler to call once the pack has been","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed. This handler is executed asynchronously on the main queue.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As soon as this method is called on a pack, the pack becomes invalid; any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attempt to send it a message will result in an exception being thrown. If an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error occurs and the pack cannot be removed, do not attempt to reuse the pack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object. Instead, if you need continued access to the pack, suspend all packs"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and use the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method to obtain valid pointers to all the packs."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To detect when any call to this method results in a pack being removed, observe","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"KVO change notifications on the shared offline storage object’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" key","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path. Removals from that array result in an ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSKeyValueChangeRemoval","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" change.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When you remove an offline pack, any resources that are required by that pack,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but not other packs, become eligible for deletion from offline storage. Because"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the backing store used for offline storage is also used as a general purpose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cache for map resources, such resources may not be immediately removed if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implementation determines that they remain useful for general performance of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map."}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:"]}],"metadata":{"title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(im)removePack:withCompletionHandler:","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/reloadPacks":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/reloadpacks","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"reloadPacks"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Forcibly, asynchronously reloads the "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property. At some point after this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is called, the pointer values of the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property change, even if the underlying data for these packs has not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changed. If this method is called while a pack is actively downloading, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"behavior is undefined."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"reloadPacks"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","type":"topic","title":"reloadPacks","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/removePack:withCompletionHandler:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","title":"MLNOfflinePack","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackremovalcompletionhandler","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A block to be called once an offline pack has been completely invalidated and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"removed."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"symbol"}}}